$interpreted: Overheated Believer: It's so darn hot! Is the Holy Maiden going to come out or what!?
Impatient Believer: Yeah! The Shrine's not only a bunch of liars, now they've learned how to slack off!
Senior Cleric: Holy Maiden, should we just cancel...
Misa: No! The Mission Conference has always been held at this time. If we cancel it for no reason, does that not mean that we are lacking in confidence?
Misa: Don't mention it again!
Senior Cleric: Yes...
Senior Cleric: ...Here is your medicine. It is the last one.
Misa: The last one...
Senior Cleric: The High Priest has always prepared it himself, so no one knows the ingredients...
Impatient Believer: We can't wait any longer! If it doesn't start, I'm leaving!
Misa: (...You can do this, Misa!)
Misa: ...*breathes*...
Misa: People of the Snake God, we are gathered here today——
Fidgety Believer: ——Don't preach to us!
Fidgety Believer: We just want to know if you're the real deal. Well, are you!?
Misa: ...Rude disciple! What is this? You dare act this way at the Sacred Mission Conference——
Fidgety Believer: ——My brother is almost dead!
Fidgety Believer: He was attacked by those monsters during the wall of wind incident. The doctor said...there's nothing that can be done.
Misa: How could this be...
Fidgety Believer: You're the person that he adores the most, Holy Maiden Misa!
Fidgety Believer: It's your fault he's hurt anyway. If you're real, then save him!
Misa: Of course, all I need is to eat...
Misa: (Oh no, that was the last one!)
Misa: (Without the medicine, I have no powers and I'm no Holy Maiden...It's never been real...!)
Fidgety Believer: Speak! Finish what you were saying already!
Misa: I......
Nervous Believer: Hey, your brother isn't breathing! Is he...is he dead!?
Fidgety Believer: Chuck! Chuck!
Fidgety Believer: You bastard, who said you could die like this...Useless! Trash! Brother, I still haven't...*sob*...*sob*...!
Misa: I-I...I just...I haven't made a decision...
Misa: I didn't mean to, but I, I can't——
Impatient Believer: I knew it! Those miracles were all a bunch of lies! You and that slithery Devious tricked us!
Cleric: Such impudence! How dare you speak such words to the Holy Maiden!?
Impatient Believer: Oh, lookie here. The perpetrator playing the victim! It's about time to settle the score with you, Shrine scum!
Senior Cleric: Holy Maiden, you have no energy. We'll block them. You must go!
Fidgety Believer: ...There you are.
Misa: You...what do you want?
Fidgety Believer: I couldn't find Devious. You better pay back what he owes to my brother!
Misa: Wah——!
???: Swallow it!
Misa: What is this!? I don't...
Misa: Wait, this feeling...is this——
???: Indeed. What I gave you is very much like Devious' medicine.
???: Try and see if the effects are the same..."Holy Maiden".
Misa: ...My powers have returned. It's...it's the same...
Misa: Who are you!? How do you have the High Priest's medicine?
???: Look again. You don't recognize me?
Misa: Eh?
Misa: The injury on your face is so severe. I don't know anyone with such a serious injury...
???: It seems that you recall. Long time no see. Hello...Misa.
Misa: ——Joshua!?
